DESCRIPTION

     Rashumon is a multi-lingual graphic word processor which contains
     English, Hebrew, Arabic and Russian (as well as other languages)
     support.  Rashumon supports multiple fonts (bit-mapped and
     scalable), including proportional spacing.  It also has fast
     scrolling and editing speed.  Rashumon is user friendly with a
     graphic user interface.  It has full math support, IFF and ASCII
     import and export capability as well as an option for creating
     Scala Lingua scripts.

	The studen't version for Rashumon is identical to the commercial 
	one except for the price and the docomentation which is on a text 
	file instead of a printed manual.

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS

	OS 2.04 and higher

